Shakma;;1990;;R;;Horror,Sci-Fi,Thriller;;5.0;;Hugh Parks,Tom Logan;;Christopher Atkins,Amanda Wyss,Ari Meyers,Roddy McDowall,Robb Edward Morris,Tre Laughlin,Greg Flowers,Ann Kymberlie,Donna Jarrett,Jack V. Butler,Typhoon,Sandra Von Johnson;;An experimental drug that is supposed to reduce aggression has the opposite effect on a baboon that is being experimented on by a group of medical students and their professor. While they are playing a fantasy role-playing game in their research facility, the baboon escapes and begins hunting them down.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0100589/